# aws-parallelcluster_compute_fleet_status (Data Source)

Describe the status of the compute fleet.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "aws-parallelcluster_compute_fleet_status" "example" {
  cluster_name = var.cluster_name
  region       = var.region
}
```
